OL,3,CRotherham grooming gang survivors have
OL,4,C'no faith' in South Yorkshire Police
OL,6,FSix women, who were sexually exploited
OL,7,Fby gangs in Rotherham as children,
OL,8,Fclaim they were also abused by local
OL,9,Fpolice officers.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct confirmed three former South
OL,13,FYorkshire police officers had been
OL,14,Farrested and the investigation into
OL,15,Fthese allegations was continuing.
OL,17,FOne of the former officers arrested is
OL,18,Faged in his sixties and the other two
OL,19,Fare in their fifties.
