OL,3,CRotherham grooming gang survivors have
OL,4,C'no faith' in South Yorkshire Police
OL,6,F"The accounts we have heard, which we
OL,7,Fexpect are only a fraction of the full
OL,8,Fscale of abuse, are utterly
OL,9,Fharrowing," lawyer Amy Clowrey said.
OL,11,FShe has been representing survivors of
OL,12,Fabuse in Rotherham for more than a
OL,13,Fdecade.
OL,15,FMs Cowley said that they hoped "the
OL,16,Falleged abuse by police officers would
OL,17,Fbe unearthed and that there would be
OL,18,Faccountability" following criminal
OL,19,Fproceedings against the gang members
OL,20,Fand a separate investigation.
