OL,3,CRotherham grooming gang survivors have
OL,4,C'no faith' in South Yorkshire Police
OL,6,F"That never came," she said in a
OL,7,Fstatement.
OL,9,F"For years the authorities have
OL,10,Fresisted our requests for an
OL,11,Finvestigation into the alleged
OL,12,Fcriminality of police officers,
OL,13,Fdespite us providing them with the
OL,14,Faccounts of survivors."
OL,16,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct said South Yorkshire Police
OL,18,Fshould carry out the investigation
OL,19,Finto the allegations against its
OL,20,Fofficers and insisted there was no
OL,21,Fconflict of interest.
