OL,3,CRotherham grooming gang survivors have
OL,4,C'no faith' in South Yorkshire Police
OL,6,F"This is a highly sensitive and
OL,7,Fcomplex investigation and we decided
OL,8,FSYP would carry out the investigative
OL,9,Fenquiries given it has the specialist
OL,10,Fexpertise and resources," the IOPC
OL,11,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,13,F"We were assured by the force that
OL,14,Fnone of the investigating officers had
OL,15,Feither worked with any of the former
OL,16,Fofficers under investigation or were
OL,17,Fthemselves investigated as part of Op
OL,18,FLinden.
