OL,3,CRotherham grooming gang survivors have
OL,4,C'no faith' in South Yorkshire Police
OL,6,FBut Ms Cowley said survivors had "no
OL,7,Ffaith" South Yorkshire Police would do
OL,8,Fa "thorough job" of the investigation.
OL,10,F"In addition, dealing with SYP is
OL,11,Fretraumatising for them, many of our
OL,12,Fclients refuse to report offences to
OL,13,FSYP because they do not think they
OL,14,Fwill be believed and because they were
OL,15,Ftreated so badly in the past," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"This investigation must be handed
OL,19,Fover to an independent police force to
OL,20,Fensure that survivors feel confident
OL,21,Fenough to come forward."
